(146, 'widget_optimizer_front_text', 'a:30:{i:1;a:0:{}i:3;a:8:{s:7:"content";s:234:"<p style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 30px"><strong><em>"Support Groups Central is the innovator in online peer support</em><em>”</em></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: right"><em>- Customer Executive</em></p>";s:12:"padtopbottom";s:1:"5";s:11:"paddingside";s:1:"9";s:8:"parallax";s:1:"1";s:13:"content_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:10:"content_bg";s:7:"#333333";s:13:"content_bgimg";s:74:"http://peersupportsolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/LPimage1-sm.jpg";s:5:"width";N;}i:5;a:0:{}i:7;a:7:{s:7:"content";s:1984:"<h1>[toggle title="HOW WE CAN HELP"]</h1><p style="margin: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: Georgia;color: #323333"><b>Here are some of the ways we can work together if you decide that your organization should be providing peer support.</b></p><p style="margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Georgia;color: #323333"> </p><ul><li style="margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Georgia;color: #323333">TURNKEY PEER SUPPORT SERVICES: you can have us create, staff, and peer support-based services on your behalf. You provide guidance and oversight, we handle the rest.</li><li style="margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Georgia;color: #323333">INTEGRATION: you can integrate your new peer support service with other health services in your portfolio to further reduce cost and improve patient outcomes.</li><li style="margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Georgia;color: #323333">PEER SUPPORT PLATFORM: you can use our video- and chat-based HIPAA-compliant platform to offer peer support with your own team of peer specialist. We''ll still monitor the platform itself, of course. </li><li style="margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Georgia;color: #323333">STAFF AUGMENTATION: you can lean on our years of experience, and connections into the talent pool, to quickly scale your program.</li><li style="margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Georgia;color: #323333