(12627, '_transient_optimizer_pro-update-response', 'O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:11:"new_version";s:5:"0.4.5";s:4:"name";s:13:"Optimizer PRO";s:4:"slug";s:13:"optimizer_pro";s:3:"url";s:60:"https://optimizerwp.com/downloads/optimizer-pro/?changelog=1";s:12:"last_updated";s:19:"2016-08-05 04:04:58";s:8:"homepage";s:48:"https://optimizerwp.com/downloads/optimizer-pro/";s:7:"package";s:156:"https://optimizerwp.com/edd-sl/package_download/MTQ3MjkzODIzMjplOTUzZTY4YTJjMWEwMTM0ODEwOGFlOTQ0YzI3NTY4MjoyODQ6ODdkZjI0NDUzY2JjODJkN2Q1MTViZDZlYTNkOWRmYjg6";s:13:"download_link";s:156:"https://optimizerwp.com/edd-sl/package_download/MTQ3MjkzODIzMjplOTUzZTY4YTJjMWEwMTM0ODEwOGFlOTQ0YzI3NTY4MjoyODQ6ODdkZjI0NDUzY2JjODJkN2Q1MTViZDZlYTNkOWRmYjg6";s:8:"sections";a:2:{s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:9:"changelog";s:29200:"<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.4.5 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(4th August, 2016 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: <a href="https://optimizerwp.com/wordpress-theme-optimizer-update-0-4-5" target="_blank">New Widget - Dynamic Content</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Blocks New Option: Link Fields</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Woocommerce Cart menu should dropdown cart items</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Social Links position: Header + Footer &amp; Topbar + Footer</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Client''s logo has a new option to display logos in carousel.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Google Map broke after Google’s API Change. <a href="https://optimizerwp.com/wordpress-theme-optimizer-update-0-4-5/" target="_blank"><strong>Action Required, see this</strong></a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Newsletter widget was not working at all.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Beaver Builder &amp; Bbpress plugin’s text editor was not working</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Video widget YouTube not working on mobile on click:</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: YouTube api is making sites very slow, added lazy loading feature for YouTube videos.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Optimizer Child theme loads stylesheet twice</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Slider image is cut off on imac.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Lightbox was not working on portfolio galleries.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Social Widget Color override option was not working</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Single Post with Header should display the default colors from Default Page header settings instead of black</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Portfolio Preview Image was stretched in Firefox</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Portfolio Hover layout 5 doesn''t show up well on clicking the "Load More" button.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Portfolio Archive Page header should be hidden</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Portfolio aligned to left on large screens.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Center logo with simple mobile menu doesn’t work.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Menu was not displayed on landscape mode on ipad.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Static Slideshow should display a black loading screen like nivo slider</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.4.4 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(1st June, 2016 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: <a href="https://optimizerwp.com/wordpress-theme-optimizer-update-0-4-4/">Advanced inline editor in Customizer</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Newsletter Widget</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Schema Markup</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 15 More Widget Presets</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Customizer UI Enhancement</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Enhanced Boxed Layout Option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Force Display Page Header in Widgetized Pages option.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Duplicate Widget functionality.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Big Logo used to overlap with Hamburger menu on mobile.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When Sticky header was enabled, the slider was not partially visible on mobile devices.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Sticky Header was jumping up and down in iphones</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Nivo Slider alignment did not work properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Slider content vertical Position is not working on small displays.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Biography Widget background did not work properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: W3 html validation errors in Customized Widgets Pages.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Some Gallery lightbox bugs.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Hungarian Translation fix (Big Thanks to <strong>Judy Toth</strong> ).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>0.4.3 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(2nd May, 2016 )</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: <a href="https://optimizerwp.com/?p=135870&amp;preview=true" target="_blank">Ability to add 1 additional field in Contact widget.</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Ability to display Custom page as your 404 page.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Image size option Instagram, Flickr, Pinterest Widgets.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Social Widget compatibility with 33 social Sites.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 2 New Layouts for Blog Page Template.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Ability to display hamburger for topbar menu on mobile devices.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Display Category Header Image in Woocommerce Category Pages.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Pagination was not visible in Category pages and Blog page.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Responsive video shortcodes were not working inside Widgets.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Nivo slider displayed all the images under one another for a split second while loading.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Nivo Slider''s Content Alignment "Right" option was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Nivo Slider''s first image was jerking on Safari.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Video Widget''s custom video was being repeated.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Jetpack''s Portfolio tags are not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Jetpack''s Tiled gallery was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Logo Image in Sticky Header looked deformed on scroll.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Widget width feature was sometimes not working properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Optimizer''s Gallery styles were not responsive.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Custom Font was not loaded in the editor''s font select menu.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When portfolio Plugin is not installed, adding portfolio widget caused a fatal error</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Nivo Slider disappeared after activating polylang plugin.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Woocommerce Products pages sometimes displayed uneven layout.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Removed woocommerce.php and re-created everything with Woocommerce action hooks and filters to improve compatibility with other plugins.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Woocommerce Shop page''s Custom Page Header Options did not work.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Woocommerce button Styles did not apply to woocommerce shortcodes.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Infinite Scroll (Auto) was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Few Dutch translation issues.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>0.4.2 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(14th April, 2016 )</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Theme crashed in php version 5.2</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Woocommerce was not loading sometimes.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Category page with layout3 was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Sticky Header with Transparent header option displayed made the header non-transparent.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Some Menu Plugin works with free version but not with PRO.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Transparent header doesn''t work when site is boxed.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Posts Widget Navigation Arrows Incorrectly Positioned</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Some texts could not be translated using Loco Translate.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Countdown Widget had incorrect dutch translation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.4.1 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(10th April, 2016 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: <a href="https://optimizerwp.com/wordpress-theme-optimizer-0-4-1/" target="_blank">WordPress 4.5 Compatibility.</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Speed Improvement.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 9 Woocommerce dedicated options.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Duplicate Widgets feature.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Auto email Theme settings every day or week.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: H1,H2, H3, H4, H5, H6 Color Option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Video Widget default video thumbnail option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 12 Countdown widget styles.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: A "Plain" style to Single portfolio page option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Translated to 11 more languages.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Header in mobile had unwanted gap under it.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Upon creating a custom sidebar, all the about widgets of the site were reset to default.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Blocks were not lining up correctly sometimes.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Google Analytics stopped working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Password reset link was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: 3 level Submenus were not working properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Navigation was not working in Posts Widget when Layout 3 and Infinite Scroll were selected.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Vimeo &amp; Tripadvisor Social link from Customize &gt; Miscellaneous &gt; Social Links was not working</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Social links inside header was not shown in hamburger menu.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Contact Widget was not showing any error when the email address was invalid.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Woocommerce Pagination not working in Posts Widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Portfolio Share icons disable option was not work.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Portfolio Category Header Image and Description was not showing up.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Export Options wasn’t working sometimes.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Infinite Scroll (Auto) was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: SEO Yoast word was count not working when page is customized with widgets.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Numbered Pagination showed all buttons.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: In Contact page, Contact form without map did not look good.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.4.0 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(21st February, 2016 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 15 More Presets .</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Display Header on left option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Disable Smart Resize Slider Image (Mobile) option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Countdown widget background image option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Transparent Page Header Option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: New Widget Width - Three Quarters.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Hover effect option in Blocks Widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 3 New Slider types in Slider Widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Social Bookmark icon auto identify and display feature.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 2 New Single page layouts.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Font Weight options in Basic Fonts Section.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Different logo option for Frontpage header.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: PHP 7 Compatibility.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 2 New styles for Progress Bar Shortcode.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 4 New styles Pricing Shortcode.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Icon Shortcode now has predefined style options and can be linked to an external url.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Breadcrumb Shortcode.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: New Title Dividers.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: 1 New Style added to Social Bookmark Widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Background Color and Text color option added to Biography Widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>:  Title Divider option in Client logo widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Woocommerce products by categories in Posts Widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Posts Widget Pagination broke after last update.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Google Map Live customization was not work properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Custom Javascript field was not working correctly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When Customizing page with widgets, the seo options was not visible in the Page Edit screen.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Couldn''t insert single quote in Contact Page map description field.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Columns shortcodes were not working correctly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Tabs shortcode were not working correctly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When Portfolio plugin was not present, Adding Portfolio widget threw a Fatal Error..</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Menu not visible in iPad.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Icons inserted in menu is not visible in hamburger menu.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Layout 3 of Posts Widget was not working properly when there is another post widget in the page.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Portfolio posts per page was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When the logo position is set to middle and the tagline is set to hidden the tagline still showed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.8 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(1st January, 2016 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Logo can be displayed in the topbar.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Ability to Save Presets &amp; Import saved Presets on any pages.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Testimonial Widget has a new Job Title field.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Countdown widget background image option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: More styles to Lightbox Button shortcode.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Clicking on the "to top" button on mobile devices redirects to 404 page.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When the about widget is added in a customized page, all the about widgets are reset sometimes.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Customize Page doesn''t work when wordpress is japanese or special character based language..</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Radio buttons not displayed in Chrome.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Comment time was messed up.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Widget menu linking not working with some widgets.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Posts Widget''s Next/Previous Navigation not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Multiple instance of map widgets not showing up properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: 2col and 3col widgets Equal height issue.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.7 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(3rd November, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Dutch, Swedish, Polish, French Translation.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Fatal error: Uncaught exception ''Exception with message Plugin dir is not inside of WP_CONTENT_DIR.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When the about widget is added in a customized page, all the about widgets from the site gets removed.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When the content added/edited through "Text" mode the changes did not take place.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Custom Font upload threw error on some hosts.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Blog Page template pagination not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Blog Page Post thumbnails not showing up on 2nd/3rd page.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Lightbox not working in Blog page template.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Multiple instance of map widgets not showing up properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Map Shortcode not loading in blog page template.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Map Shortcode doesn''t work inside widgets.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Video widget is loading a grey box for some youtube videos.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Video Widget doesn''t display controls for some videos.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Video widget displays related videos in the end.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: In Woocommerce Shop page Sidebar couldn''t be set to "left".</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When a widget is linked to menu, clicking from other pages doesn''t do anything.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Widget content was not editable in Siteorigin Page builder..</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Pinterest Widget was not displayed correctly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: On Safari Social icon throws a white flash upon hovering over them.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Safari displayed a white flash upon hovering over the Posts (Layout1).</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Sticky header created a empty space above header in mobile devices.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Mobile Slider Content has padding on top. Causing the image to stretch.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Form Buttons on Safari Mobile looks ugly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Posts thumbnails has to be clicked twice to enter the posts(Layout 1) in Mobile.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Posts thumbnails were not clickable in Layout 1 in Mobile.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: When the resolution is over 1024 the slider content gets cut off on top.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.6 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(9th October, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Portfolio Post type Support + Portfolio Widget. <strong><a href="https://www.layerthemes.com/update-optimizer-0-3-6/" target="_blank">Read More</a>&gt;</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Easier function to add widgets to other pages.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Widget Columns (Width) Settings in each widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>:  Widget Import/Export.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Custom Font Upload.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>5 New Gallery styles.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Translated to 6 Languages.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Option to make the Background Fixed.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Disable SEO option was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: If slider image is small it was not automatically stretched to full width.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Submenu not working on IE.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Preset Didn''t work on some hosts.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Logo was not responsive on firefox</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Next/Previous Post still shows when there were no posts.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: The hamburger menu is still visible when there is no menu.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Map shortcode didnt work if there were multiples in one page.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Woocommerce Shop Page header was not displayed.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Post Widget''s Infinite Scroll didnt work on other pages..</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.5 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(17th September, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>New Slider CTA Button Styles. <a href="https://www.layerthemes.com/update-optimizer-0-3-5/" target="_blank">Read More &gt;</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Widget Linking capability for Slider CTA buttons. <a href="https://www.layerthemes.com/documentation/make-menu-linked-to-frontpage-elements/" target="_blank">Documentation &gt;</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Topbar submenu feature.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>:  Vimeo Bookmark Link in Social Bookmark icons.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Option to hide header menu.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Option to hide Site title.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Option to hide Site tagline.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> About Widget Width Option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Menu Widget Compatibility.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: more styles for Social Bookmark Widget.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Dropdown menu doesn''t work correctly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Contact page map not showing up.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Category Header Image selector not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Video not displayed in mobile version. Display the slider Image as fallback photo.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Next/previous post looks weird when there is no thumbnail attached to the post.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Sticky header not working with boxed layout.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: The Customizer Options sometimes disappear when switching to different tabs.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.4 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(3rd September, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fixed:  Last update broke Blocks Widget''s Checkbox Fields. They were not working. For full update see version 0.3.3 changelog below.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.3 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(3rd September, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong><a href="http://www.layerthemes.com/update-optimizer-0-3-3/" target="_blank">Widget Presets!</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Presets Feature. You can now Import Presets!</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Menu Background Color Option</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>:  Text Alignment Option now works with Nivo Slider.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Slider Text Alignment. You can now align Static Slide text to left, right and center.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>More Contact form options.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>New Mobile Menu type.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> About Widget Width Option.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Flickr Shortcode now has the ability to display photosets.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Hide Sidebar option isn''t working</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: If Advanced text widget has Parallax effect and placed before footer, the footer looked weird.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Menu hover color not working on frontpage</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Posts WIdget''s preview and link button display options not working</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Ajax pagination loads draft posts too.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Shortcode window was not rendering properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Map shortcode did not work.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: alt tag was not being rendered in blocks &amp; logo image.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.2 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(20th August, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>WordPress 4.3 compatibility.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Presets Feature. You can now Import Presets! <a href="https://www.layerthemes.com/update-optimizer-0-3-2/" target="_blank">Read More</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Posts Widget now has 5 Woocommerce Products Layouts!</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Footer &amp; Copyright Area Background Image</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Slider Text Alignment. You can now align Static Slide text to left, right and center.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Input fields and forms can be added in Slider Content.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Columns Shortcodes now has width parameter. You can define width of each column.</li>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Carousel Shortcode has a new Layout.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Blocks Widget now has a title field.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed: </strong>Google Analytics option was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed: </strong>The Customizer did not work when there were no pages created in your site.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed: </strong>Transparent Header color was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed: </strong>Widget title in Customizer Options showed weird characters when german dialects were added.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:  </strong>Custom Css and Custom JS converted apostrophes to \\''</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed: </strong>Contact Map Broke when there was a new line in map description field</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed: </strong>Layout 3 of Posts Widget was not functioning properly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed: </strong>Vimeo Shortcode was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Sidebar on Woocommerce Shop Page displayed twice.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed: </strong>Font family was not working in child theme.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.1 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(9th August, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added: </strong>Php 5.2 Compatibility.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> New Underline Style for Title Divider.</li>\n<li>Fixed: "Header Already Sent" error that prevented some users to login to dashboard.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Text Widget Parallax bug.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Shortcodes did not parse in Widget Title. Now you can use Shortcodes inside widget titles too.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Blocks Widget sometimes collapsed on each other.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Mobile Layout Options not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Adding Html inside Nivo Slider description fields breaks the slider.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Slider Image not visible in Touch Devices/mobiles</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Static Slideshow Responsiveness issues.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Sticky Header doesn''t work on mobile devices.</li>\n<li><strong>Enhancement:</strong> Changed the look of Comment form submit button.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.3.0 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(3rd August, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>BIG Update: Theme Options moved to Customizer. Frontpage Elements converted to widgets. Please <a href="https://www.layerthemes.com/improved-optimizer-wordpress-theme/" target="_blank">Read this</a> Before Updating the theme.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.2.3 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(4th May, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong> <strong>MAJOR BUG:</strong> Menu Links were  not clickable in previous version.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.2.2 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(4th May, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> 50 action hooks for developers.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Ability to display selected pages only on frontpage posts section.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> PHP 5.3 and 5.4 Support.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Accordion Slider Text getting cut off from the bottom.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Comment from input fields look ugly.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Static Slider looks broken on mobile and tabs if there is no slider content.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;"><strong>0.2.1 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(28th April, 2015 )</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Ability to add content in Contact page template + Sidebar on Contact page.</li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Better way to link Frontpage elements to menu. <a href="http://www.layerthemes.com/documentation/make-menu-linked-to-frontpage-elements/" target="_blank">Read Tutorial</a></li>\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Share icons on pages too. Go to Optimizer Options &gt; Social &gt; Share to enable/disable.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Slider Responsiveness.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Settings &gt; Reading &gt; Frontpage Displays &gt; Static page &gt; Posts page Not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> If there was no widgets added to sidebar it displayed an empty space.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Sidebar is not displayed on archive/search pages.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Internet explorer header image not responsive.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Blocks looked weird when the blocks size are not same.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Made the footer always sticks to the bottom even when the page is too short.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Woocommerce products not visible.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Sticky Header issue.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Slider Youtube Video Repeat field not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Disable Page Header title was not working.</li>\n<li><strong>Updated:</strong> Font Awesome icons to 4.3.0</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>0.2.0 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">(7th April, 2015 )</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Demo Preset Import Functionality.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Behance and Dribble social icons.</li>\n<li><strong>Added</strong>: Option to Hide Page Header Image in mobile.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Map is not loading in Contact page</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Static Slideshow only displays 6 images.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: Front page posts broken thumbnails.</li>\n<li><strong>Fixed</strong>: If Front page blocks are not equal they look weird.</li>\n</ul>\n";}}', 'no'),
